				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4ng-C%E1%BA%A9n/B%C3%A0n-Kh%C3%AA-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-hu%E1%BB%B3nh-ph%C3%BA/poem-9fjFSSgRC7FHC9xd4YkEQw">Bàn Khê điếu huỳnh phú - 蟠溪釣璜賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4ng-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-EpzWfGVBH2wEhP3RsbFZjA">Trần Công Cẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%E1%BA%A3n/B%E1%BA%AFc-H%C3%A0/poem-IZv2qP4V8liSTCihg0Io3w">Bắc Hà - 北河</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%E1%BA%A3n/author-Rf5MQH5zACpwcSwDnHFWvQ">Lý Trần Thản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Chu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-d%E1%BB%8Bch-c%E1%BA%ADn-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-MOOM7-TAWuClxdN33bsv0Q">Chu nguyệt đối dịch cận tự - 舟月對驛近寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/C%E1%BB%95-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-dsKQjFuWUCGClVpPQW_3_g">Cổ tự - 古寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-to%E1%BA%A1-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-b%C3%ADch/poem-8AF4qassA7lCrx9By1Jd0g">Đề toạ thượng bích - 題座上壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/author-_-n7AebzEZbDFLh7p_iY6g">Đặng Thái Thân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90inh-S%E1%BB%ADu-h%E1%BA%A1-ng%C5%A9-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%C3%A3n-giai-H%E1%BB%93-Trai-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-v%C3%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Phan-K%C3%ADnh-Ch%E1%BB%89/poem-Z306Hwt5c8VjxS4iOHvk6g">Đinh Sửu hạ ngũ nguyệt nhị thập vãn giai Hồ Trai Phạm tiên sinh vãng Quảng Trị phỏng Phan K